00:15:34.440 --> 00:15:36.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Annesine bakar mısın?

137
00:15:38.120 --> 00:15:42.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Sanatoryumdan yeni çıkmış diye duydum.
-Rahibe kıyafetini giymiş.

138
00:15:42.560 --> 00:15:45.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Hazır mıyız? Bir...
-Alman bir rahibe.

139
00:15:45.240 --> 00:15:46.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bir, iki, üç.

140
00:15:47.760 --> 00:15:48.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çok güzel.

141
00:15:49.360 --> 00:15:52.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Buraya bakalım lütfen. Hazır mıyız?

142
00:15:53.640 --> 00:15:55.640 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Harika. Teşekkür ederim.

143
00:15:56.480 --> 00:15:57.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Majesteleri?

144
00:16:09.800 --> 00:16:13.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çok güzel oldu. Hazır mıyız?

145
00:16:14.560 --> 00:16:15.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Teşekkürler.

146
00:16:16.640 --> 00:16:19.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Bu nedir?
-Benim sana hediyem.

147
00:16:22.000 --> 00:16:23.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Açabilir miyim?

148
00:16:26.560 --> 00:16:28.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Baba!

149
00:16:30.280 --> 00:16:31.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Evliliğin

150
00:16:32.680 --> 00:16:37.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
benimki kadar mutlu geçerse

151
00:16:38.280 --> 00:16:40.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
hiçbir anını kaçırmanı istemiyorum.

152
00:16:44.480 --> 00:16:46.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Lilibet? Seni bekliyorlar.

153
00:16:47.400 --> 00:16:48.280 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Teşekkür ederim.

154
00:16:49.840 --> 00:16:50.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İçine koy.

155
00:17:00.600 --> 00:17:02.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Bertie?
-Hazır mısınız?

156
00:17:04.880 --> 00:17:07.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Herkes hazır mı? Margaret?

157
00:17:08.040 --> 00:17:10.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Efendim.
-Teşekkürler.

158
00:17:30.000 --> 00:17:31.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Teşekkürler.

159
00:17:41.920 --> 00:17:45.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Kralı istiyoruz!

160
00:18:23.320 --> 00:18:25.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
ON İKİ AY SONRA

