SEKİZ AYLIK HAMİLEYKEN
SEACLIFFE PLAJI

162
00:18:30.080 --> 00:18:34.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
PHILIP VE CHARLES,
LINDISFARNE ADASI

163
00:18:34.640 --> 00:18:39.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
ANNE'İN VAFTİZİ

164
00:18:39.280 --> 00:18:44.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
AİLE FOTOĞRAFI, BALMORAL

165
00:18:44.960 --> 00:18:48.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
KÜREK TAKIMI, MALTA 1951

166
00:18:48.280 --> 00:18:54.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
KRALİYET DONANMASI
KÜREK FİNALLERİ, MALTA

167
00:18:58.960 --> 00:19:02.680 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çekin! Çekin sizi piçler!

168
00:19:30.760 --> 00:19:32.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Herkes içeri! Başlıyoruz!

169
00:19:35.600 --> 00:19:39.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Geldiğiniz için çok teşekkürler.
Harika, gelmişsiniz!

170
00:19:39.840 --> 00:19:43.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Haydi, içeri gelin.
Siz olmadan başlayamayız.

171
00:19:43.320 --> 00:19:45.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-İçeri girin beyler.
-Peki efendim.

172
00:19:45.320 --> 00:19:46.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Teşekkürler.

173
00:19:54.000 --> 00:19:55.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hanımlar ve beyler

174
00:19:55.080 --> 00:19:57.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Prenses Elizabeth Hazretleri
için sessizlik lütfen.

175
00:19:57.560 --> 00:19:58.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Teşekkürler Martin.

176
00:20:00.480 --> 00:20:02.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Hepinizin bildiği gibi

177
00:20:02.880 --> 00:20:09.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
sevgili eşim bundan böyle
Teğmen Mountbatten değil

178
00:20:09.200 --> 00:20:12.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Binbaşı Mountbatten olarak bilinecek.

179
00:20:12.960 --> 00:20:14.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çok teşekkür ederim.

180
00:20:16.160 --> 00:20:19.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sanırım bu yüzden üniformana yeni
bir altın halka eklemem gerekecek!

181
00:20:20.000 --> 00:20:23.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Yarım altın halka sevgilim.
Yarım altın halka beyler!

182
00:20:24.000 --> 00:20:25.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Buradaki en önemli iki kişiden

183
00:20:25.520 --> 00:20:29.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
sunumu yapmalarını istedim.

184
00:20:34.000 --> 00:20:36.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Alo? Charteris. Evet.

185
00:20:44.360 --> 00:20:45.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çok güzel.

186
00:20:47.960 --> 00:20:50.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İşte böyle. Aferin Charles, çok iyiydi.

187
00:20:50.240 --> 00:20:52.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Teşekkürler.

188
00:20:52.240 --> 00:20:54.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Teşekkürler.
-Londra'dan önemli bir telefon var.

189
00:21:54.800 --> 00:21:56.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Charles! Anne!

190
00:21:56.920 --> 00:21:58.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Çocuklar. Bekleyin.

191
00:22:01.840 --> 00:22:03.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeşil bekleme odasındalar efendim.

192
00:22:03.520 --> 00:22:05.000 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Tamam.
-Büyükbabam nerede?

193
00:22:05.080 --> 00:22:06.600 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Üst katta doktorların yanında.

194
00:22:06.680 --> 00:22:09.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Sen bakıcınla bekle,
biz birazdan döneceğiz.

195
00:22:10.120 --> 00:22:13.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Charles, burada bekle. Tamam mı?

196
00:22:21.520 --> 00:22:24.080 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Anne.
-Gelmene sevindim.

197
00:22:24.160 --> 00:22:26.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Duyar duymaz geldik.
-Biliyorum.

198
00:22:27.800 --> 00:22:29.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
-Çok üzüldüm efendim.
-Büyükanne.

199
00:22:29.840 --> 00:22:30.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Teşekkürler.

200
00:22:32.960 --> 00:22:34.320 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ameliyattalar.

201
00:22:35.240 --> 00:22:36.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
İki saat oldu.

202
00:22:55.680 --> 00:22:56.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Geldi.

203
00:23:02.840 --> 00:23:05.040 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Ameliyat oldukça iyi geçti.

204
00:23:05.120 --> 00:23:09.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Majestelerinin ameliyat sonrasındaki
durumu da tatmin edici.

205
00:23:15.840 --> 00:23:17.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Teşekkürler Doktor Bey.

206
00:23:18.120 --> 00:23:20.120 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bu iyi haber, değil mi?

207
00:23:20.240 --> 00:23:22.200 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Tamam. Biliyorum. 

208
00:23:22.880 --> 00:23:23.960 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Sen iyi misin?

209
00:24:04.640 --> 00:24:08.840 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
