-O adam asla oturmaz. Çıkar onu.

265
00:28:37.920 --> 00:28:39.560 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Bay Churchill Majesteleri.

266
00:28:44.840 --> 00:28:45.880 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Majesteleri.

267
00:28:47.480 --> 00:28:49.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Halk kararını verdi.

268
00:28:49.600 --> 00:28:53.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Partiniz seçimi kazandı

269
